products.name: Chase The Night Cartoon Moon Running With Owl Hoodie
products.description:
Unisex Hoodies – Designed for Everyone

Perfect for elevating casual wear with comfort and style.

Key Features:

  • Heavyweight Fabric: 8 oz/yd², ideal for chilly days.
  • Ideal Blend: 50% cotton for softness, 50% polyester for durability and wrinkle resistance.
  • Soft and Comfortable: Lightweight fabric for easy movement and all-day wear.
  • Cozy Brushed Interior: Warm feel with vibrant color options.
  • Stylish Hood: Double-layered hood with matching zipper.
  • Pouch Pocket: Keeps hands warm and stores small items.
  • Durable Ribbing: 1×1 ribbing with spandex for shape retention.
  • Comfortable Fit: Classic design suitable for various activities.
  • Colors: Available in a range of vibrant options.

Care Instructions:

  • Washing: Machine wash cold (max 30ºC/86ºF) inside out with like colors.
  • Drying: Tumble dry on low setting.
  • Avoid: Chlorine bleach (use as necessary), ironing, and dry cleaning.
